4 revenue; and to provide a continuing appropriation.
5 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATIVE ASSEMBLY OF NORTH DAKOTA:
6 SECTION 1. AMENDMENT. Section 57-39.2-26 of the North Dakota Century Code is
7 amended and reenacted as follows:
8 57-39.2-26. Allocation of revenue. (Effective through June 30, 2027)
9 Except as provided by sections 57-39.2-26.1, 57-39.2-26.2, 57-39.2-26.3, and 57-39.2-26.4,
10 and section 2 of this Ac t, all moneys collected and received under this chapter must be paid into
